MSCI World (MIWO00000PUS)

Find here information about the MSCI World index (MIWO00000PUS). Assess the MSCI World stock price and overall performance.

How Is The MSCI World Doing Today?
The MSCI World live stock price is 3,656.51.

What Is the MSCI World Ticker Symbol?
MIWO00000PUS is the ticker symbol of the MSCI World index.

Is MSCI World a Good Stock Market Index to Invest In?
MSCI World offers exposure to a diversified basket of stocks, which can be appealing for investors seeking broad market exposure. Investing in the index can be done through various methods such as purchasing individual stocks within the index or investing in exchange-traded funds (ETFs) that track the index.

To evaluate the potential across the various ETF options, users can sign up to InvestingPro, where they can assess ETF prices and other essential metrics.
